            <label/>
            <p>The most recent list can be found at the IthaGenes website (<ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://www.ithanet.eu/db/ithagenes?action=glist">http://www.ithanet.eu/db/ithagenes?action=glist</ext-link>).</p>
